{"title":"回文字符串","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":62,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-1520","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>所谓回文字符串，就是一个字符串，从左到右读和从右到左读是完全一样的，比如:</p>\n<p>aba  kllkllk  tyyt 都是。</p>\n<p>     当然，我们给你的问题不会再简单到判断一个字符串是不是回文字符串。现在要求你，给你一个字符串，可在任意位置添加字符，最少再添加几个字符，可以使这个字符串成为回文字符串。</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行给出一个字符串，长度为N，以换行符结束（0&lt;N&lt;1000）</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>输出所需添加的最少字符数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<pre>Ab3bd</pre>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<pre>2</pre>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>0&lt;N&lt;1000</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}